controller.file

Class MenuBarController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.file.MenuBarController

  • public class MenuBarController
extends java.lang.Object
    The MenuBar controller controls menu bar actions. Any time the menu bar is clicked the action is performed here. Most menu items simply bring up another view, others perform some logic
    Author:
